The embattled Kano state governor, governor Abdullahi Ganduje has reportedly donated 100 buses to President Muhammadu Buhari re-election campaign.

You do recall that he was allegedly involved in a contract scandal and has since refuted the video allegations, claiming the video was doctored.

A Facebook user Emoh Christiano shared pictures of the busses on a facebook group The Middle Belt Region.
